00:26:54.509 --> 00:26:55.844
Why do you look like that?

00:26:57.596 --> 00:26:59.806
Is Director Hwang dead?

00:27:00.307 --> 00:27:01.516
Did Baek Kitae tell you?

00:27:05.395 --> 00:27:06.647
I can't do this anymore.

00:27:08.440 --> 00:27:10.817
