00:27:22.537 --> 00:27:25.707
This only ends when Baek Kitae's caught.

00:27:26.458 --> 00:27:28.001
And that's how you stay alive.

00:27:29.878 --> 00:27:31.546
This is the last time.

00:27:31.630 --> 00:27:32.756
When's the deal?

