resold the drugs they seized.

00:34:15.367 --> 00:34:17.077
What the hell are you talking about?

00:34:17.160 --> 00:34:20.163
Look, who said that? What tip?

00:34:20.246 --> 00:34:21.873
Senior Investigator Kim Jeongwon.

00:34:22.916 --> 00:34:24.793
Investigator Oh Yejin, right?

00:34:25.752 --> 00:34:27.587
Please come with us, the two of you.

00:34:28.713 --> 00:34:29.964
Don't move an inch.

00:34:30.048 --> 00:34:31.466
I'll be back in a minute.

00:34:33.134 --> 00:34:34.177
Move!

00:34:35.136 --> 00:34:36.721
Get everything.

00:34:37.472 --> 00:34:39.140
Geez, why are you doing this?

00:34:40.892 --> 00:34:41.893
PROSECUTOR SEO GIHO

00:34:41.976 --> 00:34:45.522
You're shutting down the Narcotics Unit
because those dealers are giving you shit?

00:34:45.605 --> 00:34:47.565
It's the chief's orders!

00:34:48.066 --> 00:34:53.405
So we're going to let Baek Kitae
toy with the prosecution like this?

00:34:53.488 --> 00:34:55.949
It's just until the inspection is over!

00:34:56.032 --> 00:34:57.117
End of discussion!

00:34:57.200 --> 00:35:00.453
Just don't come into the office,
and keep your head down for a while!

00:35:00.537 --> 00:35:03.540
I'll pull your people
out of the Inspection Division somehow!

00:35:03.623 --> 00:35:05.333
All right, fine!

00:35:05.834 --> 00:35:07.794
I'll go pay the chief a visit

00:35:07.877 --> 00:35:09.671
and talk to him myself!

00:35:09.754 --> 00:35:10.964
Hey!

00:35:11.047 --> 00:35:12.048
Oh!

00:35:15.969 --> 00:35:17.053
Hey, get back inside.

00:35:17.887 --> 00:35:19.097
Get back inside!

00:35:22.350 --> 00:35:23.351
Hey.

00:35:24.060 --> 00:35:25.395
You think I haven't tried?

00:35:25.478 --> 00:35:29.232
The man didn't even flinch when I stood up
to him and threatened to quit!

00:35:29.315 --> 00:35:31.025
What the hell do you think you can do?

00:35:31.693 --> 00:35:35.655
Unless you want your people
to suffer more, keep your head down.

00:35:36.239 --> 00:35:38.491
Those bastards are coming at us hard!

00:35:42.746 --> 00:35:44.330
- But I--
- Jang.

00:35:45.707 --> 00:35:47.292
