Well, there was a fire, but…

00:40:43.296 --> 00:40:44.839
You just don't care, do you?

00:40:46.466 --> 00:40:49.510
The thing about greedy people is,
they're quick to get stupid.

00:40:51.179 --> 00:40:53.306
Doesn't matter to me
who sits in that seat.

00:40:54.140 --> 00:40:57.143
Apparently, you're the one
who's taken a liking to him.

00:40:59.062 --> 00:41:00.688
Is it because he's good-looking?

00:41:01.439 --> 00:41:03.316
What if something happens to Baek?

00:41:03.399 --> 00:41:04.650
Do you have an alternative?

00:41:04.734 --> 00:41:05.735
Why?

00:41:07.445 --> 00:41:08.654
Do you not trust him?

00:41:09.238 --> 00:41:10.615
I don't trust people.

00:41:11.741 --> 00:41:13.076
I trust what I hold.

00:41:18.081 --> 00:41:20.625
And that's why you're
the one who scares me most.

00:41:21.125 --> 00:41:23.753
Baek cares a lot
about his younger siblings.

00:41:24.420 --> 00:41:26.255
Especially his brother, Baek Kihyun.

00:41:27.173 --> 00:41:29.842
