- Really?
- I've got this, sir.

00:41:54.826 --> 00:41:56.828
The hell you do, damn commie.

00:42:03.042 --> 00:42:04.043
Hey!

00:42:05.211 --> 00:42:06.254
What are you doing?

00:42:14.846 --> 00:42:19.350
Hong must've twisted his ankle, sir.

00:42:20.143 --> 00:42:22.019
That's why he tumbled down the hill.

00:42:22.103 --> 00:42:23.563
Please don't worry about him.

00:42:26.190 --> 00:42:27.191
Get up.

00:42:30.027 --> 00:42:31.195
Take off your pack.

00:42:31.279 --> 00:42:32.321
I've got this, sir.

00:42:32.405 --> 00:42:33.406
Take off your pack.

00:42:34.198 --> 00:42:35.283
This is an order.

00:42:51.340 --> 00:42:54.844
We've got a goddamn commie
and a chickenshit.

00:42:54.927 --> 00:42:58.389
-That goddamn idiot.
-What a great fucking unit.

00:43:15.698 --> 00:43:17.742
Private Hong, it's not your watch yet.

00:43:17.825 --> 00:43:20.578
What are you doing here so early, sir?

00:43:20.661 --> 00:43:21.746
Huh?

00:43:23.206 --> 00:43:24.207
I was cold.

00:43:25.333 --> 00:43:26.584
Everyone's asleep, right?

00:43:27.251 --> 00:43:28.669
Yes, sir. They are.

00:43:29.295 --> 00:43:30.296
Good work.

00:44:10.419 --> 00:44:12.421
MILITARY POLICE

00:44:25.142 --> 00:44:26.519
One, two.

00:44:26.602 --> 00:44:27.853
One, two.

00:44:35.611 --> 00:44:37.905
Look at this little shit.
Did you just dodge?

00:44:40.074 --> 00:44:41.325
Goddamn it.

00:44:41.409 --> 00:44:43.369
How the hell did you let this happen?

00:44:43.452 --> 00:44:44.453
I'm sorry, sir!

00:44:44.537 --> 00:44:47.290
Both our jobs are on the line
if we don't contain this.

00:44:47.373 --> 00:44:48.833
-You hear me?
-Yes, sir!

00:44:48.916 --> 00:44:51.669
Keep checking on the injured
until sunrise,

00:44:51.752 --> 00:44:55.047
and if anyone else dies,
report it immediately!

00:44:58.759 --> 00:44:59.885
Yes, sir!

00:45:03.139 --> 00:45:05.349
Damn it.

00:45:06.851 --> 00:45:07.977
You little…

00:45:09.603 --> 00:45:10.980
You fucking bastard.

00:45:11.772 --> 00:45:13.441
Are you trying to screw me over?

00:45:15.318 --> 00:45:16.944
I warned you, didn't I?

00:45:18.279 --> 00:45:21.449
I told you to get that damn kid
transferred or whatever

00:45:21.532 --> 00:45:22.992
to keep him out of trouble.

00:45:23.576 --> 00:45:25.911
Hey, look at this mess.

00:45:26.829 --> 00:45:30.791
You brought this on yourself.

00:45:31.417 --> 00:45:32.418
Get it?

00:46:19.465 --> 00:46:20.466
PERSONAL RECORD

00:46:20.549 --> 00:46:22.009
BAEK KIHYUN
SEX: MALE

00:46:47.368 --> 00:46:48.369
Baek Kihyun,

00:46:49.120 --> 00:46:50.413
it's been a long time.

00:46:51.163 --> 00:46:53.207
We haven't seen each other
since graduation?

00:46:54.041 --> 00:46:56.001
Don't cut corners
just because you know me.

00:46:56.085 --> 00:46:57.169
Do what you always do.

00:46:57.253 --> 00:46:58.629
INVESTIGATION OFFICER
NAM SANGUK

00:46:58.712 --> 00:47:00.005
Still cocky as ever, huh?

00:47:00.881 --> 00:47:02.633
Because you graduated top of our class?

00:47:03.342 --> 00:47:05.302
So you think everyone's beneath you?

00:47:05.886 --> 00:47:08.180
You're Security Command now,
but you haven't changed.

00:47:08.889 --> 00:47:10.474
Cut the smart-ass act and proceed.

00:47:11.642 --> 00:47:13.018
There must be a reason they sent you.

00:47:13.102 --> 00:47:14.103
Well…

00:47:15.729 --> 00:47:17.606
I heard you testified
your company commander

00:47:17.690 --> 00:47:20.234
shot down the transfer request
for Private Hong.

00:47:20.317 --> 00:47:21.569
Is that true?

00:47:21.652 --> 00:47:23.028
I don't make things up.

00:47:23.112 --> 00:47:24.447
I said exactly what happened.

00:47:28.367 --> 00:47:29.577
You know,

00:47:29.660 --> 00:47:32.163
you really haven't changed
a bit, have you?

00:47:33.622 --> 00:47:36.083
Still condescending as fuck
when you don't know shit.

00:47:39.545 --> 00:47:40.713
Your company commander?

00:47:41.297 --> 00:47:43.966
Apparently, his uncle's
the Vice Minister of Foreign Affairs,

00:47:44.467 --> 00:47:46.802
and his father runs
Myeongjung Construction.

00:47:47.303 --> 00:47:48.929
The best way to clean up this mess

00:47:49.013 --> 00:47:51.932
is for someone
to take responsibility and step down.

00:47:52.516 --> 00:47:54.894
But it's never going to be your commander.

00:47:54.977 --> 00:47:57.188
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:47:57.271 --> 00:47:58.272
Get it?

00:47:59.356 --> 00:48:02.526
You know what hits me hard
every single day at Security Command?

00:48:04.028 --> 00:48:05.738
No matter how great you are,

00:48:06.405 --> 00:48:09.575
you can't do jack on your own.

00:48:10.242 --> 00:48:14.163
So stop acting like you're the only one
with integrity and rewrite your statement.

00:48:14.246 --> 00:48:15.748
It's not too late.

00:48:16.624 --> 00:48:18.751
If you cooperate now,
I can keep you in uniform.

00:48:22.713 --> 00:48:23.714
Hey.

00:48:24.215 --> 00:48:25.549
What are academy buddies for?

00:48:25.633 --> 00:48:27.510
We should cover each other's asses, right?

00:48:27.593 --> 00:48:31.722
So from now on,
you just need to do what I tell you.

00:48:32.306 --> 00:48:33.307
All right?

00:48:34.433 --> 00:48:38.062
You mean you want me to take the hit
instead of ruining my commander's career?

00:48:40.773 --> 00:48:41.774
Hey.

00:48:44.318 --> 00:48:47.655
I testified the way I did
because I knew you were going to do this.

00:48:48.239 --> 00:48:49.323
What?

00:48:49.406 --> 00:48:52.076
I don't want to ruin my own career either.

00:48:56.789 --> 00:48:59.208
Tell him, if he wants to use
his uncle for an easy out,

00:48:59.291 --> 00:49:02.545
he'd better rethink making me
the scapegoat and handle it properly.

00:49:03.170 --> 00:49:05.047
I'm not going down alone.

00:49:21.647 --> 00:49:22.648
Sir!

00:49:23.732 --> 00:49:25.734
Someone's here to see you, sir.

00:49:25.818 --> 00:49:27.152
He's in the visiting area.

00:49:32.366 --> 00:49:34.118
How can I believe you?

00:49:37.037 --> 00:49:38.622
It's hard to believe,
isn't it?

00:49:40.207 --> 00:49:42.459
But you know as well as I do,
Mr. Baek Kihyun.

00:49:43.335 --> 00:49:45.588
The fact that Mr. Baek Kitae has

00:49:46.171 --> 00:49:48.132
that much power at his age.

00:49:48.632 --> 00:49:51.427
Well, that doesn't just happen on its own.

00:49:54.513 --> 00:49:55.598
Your sister.

00:49:57.891 --> 00:50:00.811
Ms. Baek Soyeong is helping him
with the business.

00:50:01.395 --> 00:50:03.272
If I arrest Baek Kitae,

00:50:04.273 --> 00:50:06.191
your sister goes to prison,

00:50:06.275 --> 00:50:10.321
and you, Mr. Baek Kihyun,
might be forced out of the army too.

00:50:13.449 --> 00:50:17.578
Before that happens, you should talk
to her and get her to confess.

00:50:20.998 --> 00:50:24.835
If you could have taken my brother down
so easily, you wouldn't be here right now.

00:50:25.419 --> 00:50:27.630
The fact that you even had to come to me

00:50:27.713 --> 00:50:29.882
means you're in a tight spot, right?

00:50:31.425 --> 00:50:34.678
So bad that you, a prosecutor,
are threatening me.

00:50:40.643 --> 00:50:42.978
You're a lot like your brother.

00:50:45.022 --> 00:50:47.024
But there's one thing you don't know.

00:50:47.941 --> 00:50:50.235
I'm never going to give up.

00:50:50.319 --> 00:50:54.156
I'll make sure Baek Kitae faces the law
and pays for what he's done.

00:51:03.540 --> 00:51:04.583
Mr. Baek Kihyun!

00:51:05.876 --> 00:51:07.503
Think carefully!

00:51:12.341 --> 00:51:13.342
What's your plan?

00:51:15.010 --> 00:51:17.137
How long will you let
Jang Geonyoung run loose?

00:51:18.931 --> 00:51:21.141
I heard from the prosecution's
Inspection Division.

00:51:21.642 --> 00:51:24.019
They say they can't hold
his team much longer.

00:51:25.104 --> 00:51:26.105
Okay?

00:51:27.189 --> 00:51:29.942
If we go at him half-baked,
it'll be worse than doing nothing.

00:51:31.527 --> 00:51:32.778
So what are you thinking?

00:51:36.657 --> 00:51:37.825
I'll handle it.

00:51:37.908 --> 00:51:39.118
Hey, you…

00:51:43.288 --> 00:51:44.498
Just tell me, okay?

00:51:45.624 --> 00:51:47.668
Handle it how exactly?

00:51:52.840 --> 00:51:53.841
Come in.

00:51:57.177 --> 00:51:58.595
I'm sorry to interrupt, sir.

00:51:59.096 --> 00:52:00.097
It's urgent.

00:52:01.890 --> 00:52:03.350
What the hell are you looking at?

00:52:04.435 --> 00:52:05.853
You telling me to leave?

00:52:08.230 --> 00:52:09.273
Spit it out.

00:52:09.356 --> 00:52:11.150
What is it? Just tell me.

00:52:13.026 --> 00:52:15.362
I'm afraid there's a problem
with your brother.

00:52:16.572 --> 00:52:18.532
Security Command's launched
an investigation,

00:52:18.615 --> 00:52:19.867
and it's not looking good.

00:52:21.785 --> 00:52:22.786
What?

00:52:23.495 --> 00:52:25.706
Who's here? The KCIA? Baek's brother…

00:52:26.582 --> 00:52:28.792
What are you talking about, idiot?

00:52:40.179 --> 00:52:42.806
Well, who are you?

00:53:24.306 --> 00:53:25.307
Stand up straight.

00:53:27.100 --> 00:53:28.268
Back to your senses?

00:53:28.852 --> 00:53:29.853
Yes.

00:53:29.937 --> 00:53:31.522
Go get Baek Kihyun.

00:53:32.606 --> 00:53:33.607
Yes, sir.

00:53:54.378 --> 00:53:56.213
How did you hear about it?

00:53:56.755 --> 00:53:59.383
Did you think I wouldn't find out
if you kept quiet?

00:53:59.466 --> 00:54:01.176
I can handle this on my own.

00:54:02.886 --> 00:54:04.221
Handle it how exactly?

00:54:04.304 --> 00:54:06.181
I said, I'll handle it on my own!

00:54:24.867 --> 00:54:26.118
I told you.

00:54:28.579 --> 00:54:31.498
If you're angry at reality, get stronger.

00:54:38.589 --> 00:54:41.633
If you don't want to be
looked down on, strike first.

00:54:42.175 --> 00:54:44.803
If someone blocks your path,
get rid of them.

00:54:45.596 --> 00:54:47.139
How many times have I told you

00:54:47.222 --> 00:54:49.975
that guys with power
run the world at the end of the day?

00:54:53.687 --> 00:54:55.397
If you're done, I'll be going now.

00:54:56.064 --> 00:54:57.065
Stop.

00:54:59.234 --> 00:55:00.861
You cocky little…

00:55:04.156 --> 00:55:07.367
Your company commander will be
the one forced out, not you.

00:55:09.453 --> 00:55:12.497
Security Command will have an opening
next month, so get ready.

00:55:14.249 --> 00:55:15.292
This is power.

00:55:15.834 --> 00:55:17.044
Got it?

00:55:19.838 --> 00:55:21.757
I'm going to Vietnam next week.

00:55:23.300 --> 00:55:25.177
What the hell would you go there for?

00:55:25.260 --> 00:55:27.262
That "power" you always talk about.

00:55:28.096 --> 00:55:30.015
I figured I'd try to earn some myself.

00:55:30.098 --> 00:55:32.434
All you need to do is what I tell you!

00:55:32.517 --> 00:55:34.144
I can take care of myself!

00:55:34.227 --> 00:55:35.228
You little…

00:55:43.737 --> 00:55:45.322
So I want you

00:55:47.115 --> 00:55:49.743
to please just get your own act together.

00:55:50.243 --> 00:55:51.578
PROSECUTOR JANG GEONYOUNG

00:55:51.662 --> 00:55:53.789
Before you wreck my life
and Soyeong's too.

00:56:09.096 --> 00:56:10.347
Ms. Oh.

00:56:11.139 --> 00:56:12.683
What are you doing out here?

00:56:12.766 --> 00:56:14.851
Mr. Jang, where have you been?

00:56:15.769 --> 00:56:17.521
I went to see Baek Kihyun.

00:56:18.146 --> 00:56:19.147
Baek Kihyun?

00:56:19.856 --> 00:56:21.358
Things must've been rough.

00:56:22.693 --> 00:56:23.694
No, it's okay.

00:56:23.777 --> 00:56:26.071
Appreciate the effort.
Let's get inside.

00:56:28.573 --> 00:56:29.574
Well,

00:56:30.200 --> 00:56:33.578
why did you go to see Baek Kihyun, sir?

00:56:36.289 --> 00:56:38.417
Thought I'd stir up Baek Kitae too.

00:56:39.918 --> 00:56:42.421
We've got to hit back
just as hard as he hit us.

00:56:42.504 --> 00:56:45.048
So you're not giving up?

00:56:46.883 --> 00:56:48.385
Why would I give up?

00:56:48.927 --> 00:56:50.804
It's my job to catch criminals.

00:56:50.887 --> 00:56:54.182
You haven't eaten yet, right?
Let's eat first and get our strength back.

00:56:54.975 --> 00:56:56.893
Where's Mr. Kim?

00:56:56.977 --> 00:56:57.978
I'm not sure.

00:56:58.478 --> 00:56:59.896
He said he'd be here soon.

00:56:59.980 --> 00:57:02.357
But I think we ran out of rice.

00:57:02.441 --> 00:57:04.025
Should I cook some ramyeon?

00:57:05.485 --> 00:57:08.071
Shoot. We're out of ramyeon, too.

00:57:08.905 --> 00:57:10.449
I'll run out and get some.

00:57:10.532 --> 00:57:13.452
Oh, no. I'll go, sir.

00:57:13.535 --> 00:57:14.619
I'll be right back.

00:57:26.506 --> 00:57:27.632
Take care.

00:57:29.176 --> 00:57:30.177
Oh, man.

00:57:30.969 --> 00:57:32.137
It started raining.

00:57:40.228 --> 00:57:43.023
I won't live as cattle.

00:57:43.106 --> 00:57:44.691
I'll be the one with power.

00:57:47.110 --> 00:57:49.404
I'll make the herd kneel before me,

00:57:50.405 --> 00:57:52.908
drag down anyone more powerful than me,

00:57:54.034 --> 00:57:56.328
and change the world in the end.

00:58:06.379 --> 00:58:08.548
- Ms. Oh, you're here alone?
- Yes.

00:58:08.632 --> 00:58:11.176
- Where's Mr. Jang?
- He went to get some ramyeon.

00:58:11.259 --> 00:58:12.511
Hey, the water's boiling.

00:58:16.389 --> 00:58:17.766
Man, I'm exhausted.

00:58:30.987 --> 00:58:32.405
That's just the way it is.

00:58:33.281 --> 00:58:34.449
The world has always been

00:58:34.950 --> 00:58:36.827
a battlefield for the powerful.

01:01:11.940 --> 01:01:13.942
Translated by Yoonjung Song